<h1>Miscellaneous Items on Drugs and Drug Policy</h1>

<p>Items not elsewhere classified</p>

<hr>

<p><img src="../graphics/golddot1.gif" width="22" height="22"><a
href="http://turnpike.net/~jnr/wodarts.htm">War on Drugs Articles
</a>- A collection of articles about the War on Some Drugs. </p>

<p><a href="sciurin.htm">The &quot;Scientific&quot; Justification
for Urine Testing - Part 1</a></p>

<p><a href="sciurin2.htm">The &quot;Scientific&quot;
Justification for Urine Testing - Part 2</a></p>

