<p><font size="3"></font>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size="3"></font>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size="3">PRACTICE PARAMETER SUBJECT: MEDICAL PAIN
MANAGEMENT</font></p>

<p><font size="3">Endorsed on October 14, 1994, under the
authority of s. 408.02, Florida</font></p>

<p><font size="3">Statutes</font></p>

<p><font size="3"></font>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size="3">NO. GUIDE GUIDELINE ORDER FROM COST</font></p>

