<BLOCKQUOTE>
by Robert Hunter, Chapter 7 of <I>The Storming of the Mind, </I>McClelland and Stewart Ltd., &copy;Robert Hunter 1971. An early, prescient, and still valuable overview of the role of psychedelic drugs in the cultural changes of the 1960's.
